items.name: Forecasting-SP500-Realised-Volatility
items.description: Forecasting S&P 500 realized volatility using econometric and machine-learning models under a strict walk-forward framework, highlighting the role of nonlinear interactions and regime dependence.

items.name: ptmlib
items.description: PTMLib (Pendragon Tools for Machine Learning) is a set of utilities for use with Machine Learning frameworks such as Scikit-Learn and TensorFlow.
